* Interface types

- Abstract
- Define (possibly empty) set of method signatures
- Values of _any_type_ that implement all methods of an interface can be assigned to a variable of that interface.

Examples:

	interface{}  // empty interface

	interface {
		String() string
	}

	interface {
		Len() int
		Swap(i, j int)
		Less(i, j int) bool
	}


